#: _posts/2026-03-05-leyden-2.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "How we integrated Project Leyden into Quarkus"
msgstr "我们如何将莱登项目集成到 Quarkus 中"

#: _posts/2026-03-05-leyden-2.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"You might have read our first post about Project Leyden and the new "
"perspective it brought, but how did we actually integrate it into Quarkus? "
"In this post, we share our journey and the improvements we made along the "
"way."
msgstr ""
"你可能已经读过我们第一篇关于莱登项目及其带来的新视角的文章，但我们究竟是如何将其集成到 Quarkus "
"中的呢？在这篇文章中，我们将分享我们的心路历程和一路走来的改进。"

#: _posts/2026-03-05-leyden-2.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Quarkus has long supported both JVM and native image modes, each optimized "
"for different trade-offs.\n"
"Native image delivers unmatched startup and footprint.\n"
"JVM mode offers peak throughput, dynamic capabilities, and a mature tooling "
"ecosystem."
msgstr ""
"Quarkus 长期以来一直支持 JVM 和本地镜像模式，每种模式都针对不同的权衡进行了优化。原生镜像提供无与伦比的启动和占用空间。JVM "
"模式提供峰值吞吐量、动态功能和成熟的工具生态系统。"

#: _posts/2026-03-05-leyden-2.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Quarkus continues to improve and work well with native-image,\n"
"and lately Project Leyden enabled us to strengthen the JVM side of that "
"equation."
msgstr "Quarkus 不断改进，并与原生图像良好配合，最近的莱登项目使我们能够加强 JVM 方面的能力。"

#: _posts/2026-03-05-leyden-2.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"We shared our excitement about Project Leyden and how it gave us a new "
"perspective on Java application startup performance in a previous https://"
"quarkus.io/blog/leyden-1/[blog post]."
msgstr ""
"在上一篇 link:https://quarkus.io/blog/leyden-1/[博文] 中，我们分享了对 Project Leyden "
"的兴奋之情，以及它如何让我们对 Java 应用程序的启动性能有了新的认识。"

#: _posts/2026-03-05-leyden-2.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"In this post, we want to share our journey integrating Project Leyden into "
"Quarkus, and how we made this integration both efficient and easy to use for "
"our users."
msgstr ""
"在这篇文章中，我们将与大家分享将 Project Leyden 集成到 Quarkus 中的过程，以及我们是如何使这种集成既高效又便于用户使用的。"

#: _posts/2026-03-05-leyden-2.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Acknowledgements"
msgstr "致谢"

