msgstr ""
"首先，我们要感谢 IBM 的 OpenJDK "
"团队在莱登项目上所做的工作，以及我们与他们进行的多次讨论，这些讨论对我们理解莱登项目并确定如何将其最好地集成到 Quarkus "
"中起到了重要作用，他们是（按字母顺序排列）：Maria Arias de Reyna Dominguez、Andrew Dinn 和 Ashutosh "
"Mehra。"

#: _posts/2026-03-05-leyden-2.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"More broadly, we would like to thank everyone contributing to Project Leyden."
""
msgstr "更广泛地说，我们要感谢为莱顿项目做出贡献的所有人。"

#: _posts/2026-03-05-leyden-2.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Project Leyden is still evolving, and we look forward to seeing what they "
"are preparing for Java 27 and beyond."
msgstr "莱登项目仍在不断发展，我们期待看到他们为 Java 27 及以后准备的内容。"

#: _posts/2026-03-05-leyden-2.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Finally, special thanks to Sanne Grinovero for introducing us to the Leyden "
"team at just the right time, and for his insights and valuable feedback on "
